Combine @butter{1%cup}, @packed brown sugar{1.25%cup}, @granulated sugar{1/2%cup}, @eggs{2}, @milk{2%Tbsp}, @vanilla{2%tsp}, @flour{1.75%cups}, @baking soda{1%tsp}, @rolled oats{2.5%cup}, and @chocolate chips{2%cups} and bake for 8 to ~{10%minutes} at 365°F.

!!! tip
    For more flavor, toast the oats first! See [Toasted Rolled Oats](../ingredients/toasted-rolled-oats.md) for instructions.
